		<section name="Preamble">
		<p><b>NOTE: The official repository is available in a later version. If you want to share your work or get support for your company please <a href="mailto:martin.eisengardt@googlemail.com?subject=Repository access">contact us directly</a>.</b></p>
		
		<p>We require a minimum of organization to let you join the php-maven repository. That means that you must already be registered and
		have validated your email address. Without this validation we do not respect your request. Ensure that the email address is valid and
		that it is not a temporary address. We won&apos;t publish the email address in any way but keep in mind that it may be published if you
		use this email address in your pom, your sources or during svn/git commits.</p>
		
